{"tid":675966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧擔心死後遭赫魯曉夫式鞭屍清算","createTime":"2018-05-24T03:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T04:18:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2708ef811a750d0a7791b0822d52e7e5c789970b","tid":675966,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399899&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvh4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=f8e9b82f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399899&h=6f593363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399899</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月24日 <br />\n<br />\n鄧擔心死後遭赫魯曉夫式鞭屍清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/a0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2Fa0203a.gif&h=df72066f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n鮑彤指出，趙紫陽認為北京學生有權悼胡，令鄧小平擔心，趙在他死後會變成蘇共前領袖赫魯曉夫（Nikita Khrushchev，圖）。相信赫魯曉夫之所以令鄧小平感到恐懼，是因為赫魯曉夫掌握大權之後做的第一件大事，就是發起「去史太林運動」，全面清算其前任史太林（Joseph Stalin），更將其遺體移出列寧墓，繼而鞭屍，事件當年轟動整個蘇聯。<br />\n<br />\n赫魯曉夫是前蘇聯最高領導人，蘇共1956年2月14日至25日召開第二十次代表大會，他在最後一天淩晨召開的秘密會議上，連續發表4小時演說《關於個人崇拜及其後果》，抨擊史太林在位期間的嚴重錯誤，揭開「去史太林運動」，蘇聯逐步實行去史太林化。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n睹胡耀邦心臟病發　江澤民送藥救回<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n建制投反對票　毋忘六四議案遭否決<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睹胡耀邦心臟病發　江澤民送藥救回<br />\n<br />\n建制投反對票　毋忘六四議案遭否決<br />\n<br />\n鮑彤爆六四黑幕　指矛頭對着趙紫陽「鄧小平個人謀劃的政變」"},{"pid":"4ce1ffeb9faef0e7307c83485be87940642d0608","tid":675966,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"唔係真係鞭屍<br />\n<br />\n只係推佢出烈陵墓 火化"},{"pid":"50b1a639088deb12e492a2dea2dcc31305c7c856","tid":675966,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"Bin"},{"pid":"6e17fad6458c03c767306279fea631c981e67d69","tid":675966,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"篇野有啲位錯<br />\n上個post有講<br />\n<br />\n鮑彤爆六四黑幕　指矛頭對着趙紫陽 「鄧小平個人謀劃的政變」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/675861/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/675861/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}